characters.name: Amber
characters.title: Outrider of the Knights of Favonious
characters.description: Always energetic and full of life, Amber's the best - albeit only - Outrider of the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Sharpshooter
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, flames will accumulate on the arrowhead. A fully charged flaming arrow will deal Pyro DMG.

talents.name: Explosive Puppet
talents.description: Baron Bunny continuously taunts the enemy, drawing their fire. Baron Bunny's HP scales with Amber's Max HP.When destroyed or when its timer expires, Baron Bunny explodes, dealing AoE Pyro DMG.

talents.name: Fiery Rain
talents.description: Fires of a shower of arrows, dealing continuous AoE Pyro DMG.

characters.name: Lisa
characters.title: Witch of Purple Rose
characters.description: The languid but knowledgeable Librarian of the Knights of Favonius who was deemed by Sumeru Academia to be their most distinguished graduate in the past two centuries.

talents.name: Lightning Touch
talents.description: Perform up to 4 lightning attacks that deal Electro DMG.

talents.name: Violet Arc
talents.description: Channels the power of lightning to sweep bothersome matters away. Releases a homing Lightning Orb. On hit, it deals Electro DMG, and applies a stack of Conductive status (Max 3 stacks) to enemies in a small AoE.

talents.name: Lightning Rose
talents.description:
Summons a Lightning Rose that unleashes powerful lightning bolts, launching surrounding enemies and dealing Electro DMG.

The Lightning Rose will continuously emit lightning to knock back enemies and deal Electro DMG for so long as it persists.

characters.name: Kaeya
characters.title: Cavalry Captain of the Knights of Favonius
characters.description: An accomplished swordsman and a strategic thinker in the Knights of Favonius, rumored to hail from beyond Mondstadt.

talents.name: Ceremonial Bladework
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Frostgnaw
talents.description: Unleashes a frigit blast, dealing Cryo DMG to enemies in front of Kaeya.

talents.name: Glacial Waltz
talents.description:
Coalescing the frost in the air, Kaeya summons 3 icicles that revolve around him.

These icicles will follow the character around and deal Cryo DMG to enemies in their path for so long as they persist.

characters.name: Barbara
characters.title: Deaconess of the Church of Favonius
characters.description: She is the deaconess of the Church of Favonius and a prominent "idol" after learning about them from the intrepid adventurer Alice.

talents.name: Whisper of Water
talents.description: Performs up to 4 water splash attacks that deal Hydro DMG.

talents.name: Let the Show Begin
talents.description: Summons water droplets resembling musical notes that form a Melody Loop, dealing Hydro DMG to surrounding opponents and applying the Wet status to them.

talents.name: Shining Miracle
talents.description: Heals your own party members and nearby teammates for a large amount of HP that scales with Barbara's Max HP.

characters.name: Bennett
characters.title: Leader of Benny's Adventure Team
characters.description: An orphan discovered by an elderly adventurer as a baby, Bennett was raised in Mondstadt's Adventurers' Guild. He is the one and only member of "Benny's Adventure Team," as everyone else left the team after experiencing the constant misfortune that follows him.

talents.name: Strike of Fortune
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Passion Overload
talents.description: Bennett puts all his fire and passion for adventuring into his sword. Results may vary based on how fired up he is...

talents.name: Fantastic Voyage
talents.description: Bennett performs a jumping attack that deals Pyro DMG, creating an Inspiration Field. Provide HP regeneration based on Bennett's max HP and ATK bonus based on Bennet's Base ATK

characters.name: Fischl
characters.title: Prinzessin der Verurteilung
characters.description: She is an investigator for Mondstadt's Adventurers' Guild, accompanied by the night raven Oz. A daring adventurer with seemingly outlandish theories that happen to turn out to be true, she claims to hail from a world beyond Teyvat.

talents.name: Bolts of Downfall
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, the dark lightning spirits of Immernachtreich shall heed the call of their Prinzessin and indwell the enchanted arrowhead. When fully indwelt, the Rachsüchtig Blitz shall deal immense Electro DMG.

talents.name: Nightrider
talents.description: Summons Oz. The night raven forged of darkness and lightning descends upon the land, dealing Electro DMG in a small AoE. For the ability's duration, Oz will continuously attack nearby opponents with Freikugel.

talents.name: Midnight Phantasmagoria
talents.description: Summons Oz to spread his twin wings of twilight and defend Fischl. Fischl takes on Oz's form, greatly increasing her Movement Speed. Strikes nearby opponents with lightning, dealing Electro DMG to opponents she comes into contact with.

characters.name: Xiangling
characters.title: Head Chef of the Wanmin Restaurant
characters.description: She is the Head Chef at the Wanmin Restaurant and runs it alongside her father Chef Mao. As a chef, Xiangling isn't afraid to try out different recipes or "exotic" ingredients, making her dishes sometimes quite unique.

talents.name: Dough-Fu
talents.description: Performs up to five consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Guoba Attack
talents.description: Summons Guoba, who will continuously breathe fire at opponents, dealing AoE Pyro DMG.

talents.name: Pyronado
talents.description: Displaying her mastery over both fire and polearms, Xiangling sends a Pyronado whirling around her. The Pyronado will move with your character for the ability's duration, dealing Pyro DMG to all opponents in its path.

characters.name: Qiqi
characters.title: Pharmacist, Bubu Pharmacy
characters.description: Resurrected as a zombie by the adepti, she has ended up in Baizhu's care and now works at Bubu Pharmacy in Liyue Harbor.

talents.name: Ancient Sword Art
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Adeptus Art: Herald of Frost
talents.description: Using the Icevein Talisman, Qiqi brings forth the Herald of Frost, dealing Cryo DMG to surrounding opponents. On hit, Qiqi's Normal and Charged Attacks regenerate HP for your own party members and nearby teammates based on Qiqi's ATK.

talents.name: Adeptus Art: Preserver of Fortune
talents.description: Qiqi releases the adeptus power sealed within her body, marking nearby opponents with a Fortune-Preserving Talisman that deals Cryo DMG. When opponents affected by this Talisman take DMG, the character that dealt this DMG regenerates HP.

characters.name: Chongyun
characters.title: Banisher of Evil and Rumors Thereof
characters.description: Born with an excess of yang (positive) energy, Chongyun has become a highly effective exorcist in Liyue — so effective to the point where he hasn't seen a spirit himself, as they immediately flee when he approaches.

talents.name: Demonbane
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes. Drains Stamina over time to perform continuous spinning attacks against all nearby opponents. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Spirit Blade: Chonghua's Layered Frost
talents.description: Chongyun strikes the ground with his greatsword, causing a Cryo explosion in a circular AoE in front of him that deals Cryo DMG. After a short delay, the cold air created by the Cryo explosion will coalesce into a Chonghua Frost Field.

talents.name: Spirit Blade: Cloud-Parting Star
talents.description: Performing the secret hand seals, Chongyun summons 3 giant spirit blades in mid-air that fall to the earth one by one after a short delay, exploding as they hit the ground.

characters.name: Mona
characters.title: Enigmatic Astrologer
characters.description: An astrologist of knowledgeable skill and high pride, Mona has settled in Mondstadt to avoid suffering the ire of her master after unwittingly reading the latter's diary.

talents.name: Ripple of Fate
talents.description: Performs up to 4 water splash attacks that deal Hydro DMG. When Charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal AoE Hydro DMG.

talents.name: Phantom
talents.description: Creates an illusory Phantom of Fate from coalesced waterspouts. The phantom continuously taunts nearby opponents, attracting their fire and deals Hydro DMG to nearby opponents. When its duration expires, the Phantom explodes, dealing AoE Hydro DMG.

talents.name: Stellaris Phantasm
talents.description: Mona summons the sparkling waves and creates a reflection of the starry sky, applying the Illusory Bubble status to opponents in a large AoE. This trap applies wet status and renders weaker opponents immobile.

characters.name: Keqing
characters.title: Yuheng of the Liyue Qixing
characters.description: As the Yuheng of the Liyue Qixing, she is someone who seeks her own answers instead of idly letting chaos run amok in Liyue. She chooses her own path with her own power and ability, instead of letting the gods determine her fate.

talents.name: Yunlai Swordsmanship
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Stellar Restoration
talents.description: Hurls a Lightning Stiletto that annihilates her opponents like the swift thunder. When the Stiletto hits its target, it deals Electro DMG to opponents in a small AoE, and places a Stiletto Mark on the spot hit.

talents.name: Starword Sword
talents.description: Keqing unleashes the power of lightning, dealing Electro DMG in an AOE. She then blends into the shadow of her blade, striking a series of thunderclap-blows to nearby opponents simultaneously.

characters.name: Diluc
characters.title: Master of the Dawn Winery
characters.description: Born into the affluent Ragnvindr Clan, Diluc is the current owner of the Dawn Winery and a nobleman of high esteem in Mondstadt. While a past incident caused him to split ways with the Knights of Favonius, he continues to protect Mondstadt in his own way.

talents.name: Tempered Sword
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous slashes. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Searing Onslaught
talents.description: Performs a forward slash that deals Pyro DMG. This skill can be consecutively used 3 times. Enters CD if not cast again within a short period.

talents.name: Dawn
talents.description: Releases intense flames to knock back nearby opponents. The flames then converge into the weapon, summoning a Phoenix that flies forward, damaging all opponents in its path. The Phoenix explodes upon reaching its destination. The searing flames that run down his blade cause it to be infused with Pyro.

characters.name: Beidou
characters.title: Queen of the Crux Fleet
characters.description: She is the captain of The Crux, a renowned crew in Liyue. Besides her capabilities as a fleet captain and her immense strength, many in Liyue know her for her lack of fear towards the Tianquan of the Liyue Qixing, Ningguang.

talents.name: Oceanborne
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive strikes. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous slashes. At the end of the sequence, perform a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Tidecaller
talents.description: Nothing to worry about. Should anyone raise a hand against her or her men, she will avenge it ten-fold with sword and thunder. Accumulating the power of lightning, Beidou swings her blade forward fiercely, dealing Electro DMG. When charged, Beidou lifts her weapon up as a shield. Max DMG absorbed scales off Beidou's Max HP.

talents.name: Stormbreaker
talents.description: Recalling her slaying of the great beast Haishan, Beidou calls upon that monstrous strength and the lightning to create a Thunderbeast's Targe around herself, dealing Electro DMG to nearby opponents.

characters.name: Jean
characters.title: Acting Grand Master of the Knights of Favonius
characters.description: The older sister of Barbara, and a descendant of the prestigious Gunnhildr Clan, Jean is the Acting Grand Master of the Knights of Favonius. She is always busy handling unrest across Mondstadt and tirelessly working to maintain the City of Freedom.

talents.name: Favonius Bladework
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of stamina to launch an opponent using the power of wind. Launched opponents will slowly fall to the ground.

talents.name: Gale Blade
talents.description: Focusing the might of the formless wind around her blade, Jean releases a miniature storm, launching opponents in the direction she aims at. At the cost of continued stamina consumption, Jean can command the whirlwind to pull surrounding opponents and objects towards her front.

talents.name: Dandelion Breeze
talents.description: Calling upon the wind's protection, Jean creates a swirling Dandelion Field, launching surrounding opponents. At the same time, she instantly regenerates a large amount of HP for all party members. The amount of HP restored scales off Jean's ATK.

characters.name: Venti
characters.title: Anemo Archon | Singer of Skyward Sonnets
characters.description: He is a free-spirited, wine-loving bard in Mondstadt and the current mortal vessel of Barbatos, the Anemo Archon.

talents.name: Divine Marksmanship
talents.description: Performs up to 6 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, favorable winds will accumulate on the arrowhead. A fully charged wind arrow will deal Anemo DMG.

talents.name: Skyward Sonnet
talents.description: Summons a Wind Domain at the opponent's location, launching opponents into the air. When charged, summons an even larger Wind Domain with Venti as the epicenter, launching affected opponents into the air. After unleashing the ability, Venti rides the wind into the air.

talents.name: Wind's Grand Ode
talents.description: Fires off an arrow made of countless coalesced winds, creating a huge Stormeye that sucks in opponents and deals continuous Anemo DMG. If the Stormeye comes into contact with Hydro/Pyro/Cryo/Electro, it will deal additional elemental DMG of that type.

characters.name: Klee
characters.title: Spark Knight

weapon.signature: Lost Prayer to the Sacred Winds

characters.description: Always energetic and full of life, Amber's the best - albeit only - Outrider of the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Kaboom!
talents.description: Throws things that go boom when they hit things! Performs up to 3 explosive attacks, dealing AoE Pyro DMG.

talents.name: Jumpy Dumpty
talents.description: Jumpy Dumpty is tons of boom-bang-fun! When thrown, Jumpy Dumpty bounces thrice, igniting and dealing AoE Pyro DMG with every bounce. On the third bounce, the bomb splits into many mines. The mines will explode upon contact with opponents.

talents.name: Sparks 'n' Splash
talents.description: Klee's Blazing Delight! For the duration of this ability, continuously summons Sparks 'n' Splash to attack nearby opponents, dealing AoE Pyro DMG.

characters.name: Ningguang
characters.title: Lady of the Jade Chamber

weapon.signature: Lost Prayer to the Sacred Winds

characters.description: The Tianquan of the Liyue Qixing and owner of the floating Jade Chamber in the skies of Liyue, Ningguang is a mogul who shakes the very foundations of business circles.

talents.name: Sparkling Scatter
talents.description: Shoots gems that deal Geo DMG. On hit, this grants Ningguang 1 Star Jade. When charged, consumes a certain amount of stamina to fire off a giant gem. If Ningguang has any Star Jades, unleashing a Charged Attack will cause the Star Jades to be fired at the enemy as well.

talents.name: Jade Screen
talents.description: Ningguang creates a Jade Screen out of gold, obsidian and her great opulence, dealing AoE Geo DMG. Blocks opponents' projectiles. Endurance scales based on Ningguang's Max HP. Only one Jade Screen may exist at any one time

talents.name: Starshatter
talents.description: Gathering a great number of gems, Ningguang scatters them all at once, sending homing projectiles at her opponents. If Starshatter is cast when a Jade Screen is nearby, the Jade Screen will fire additional gem projectiles at the same time.

characters.name: Noelle
characters.title: Maid of the Knights of Favonius
characters.description: Always energetic and full of life, Amber's the best - albeit only - Outrider of the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Favonius Bladework: Maid
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous spinning attacks against all nearby opponents. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash

talents.name: Breastplate
talents.description: Summons protective stone armor, dealing Geo DMG to surrounding opponents and creating a shield. The shield's DMG Absorption scales based on Noelle's DEF.

talents.name: Sweeping Time
talents.description: Gathering the strength of stone around her weapon, Noelle strikes the opponents surrounding her within a large AoE, dealing Geo DMG. The attack converts attack DMG to Geo DMG that cannot be overridden by any other elemental infusion and increases ATK that scales based on her DEF.

characters.name: Razor
characters.title: Legend of Wolvendom
characters.description: Always energetic and full of life, Amber's the best - albeit only - Outrider of the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Steel Fang
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes. Drains Stamina over time to perform continuous spinning attacks against all nearby opponents. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Claw and Thunder
talents.description: Hunts his prey using the techniques taught to him by his master and his lupical. Swings the Thunder Wolf Claw, dealing Electro DMG to opponents in front of Razor. Upon striking an opponent, Razor will gain an Electro Sigil, which increases his Energy Recharge rate.

talents.name: Lightning Fang
talents.description: Summons the Wolf Within, which deals Electro DMG to all nearby opponents. This clears all of Razor's Electro Sigils, which will be converted into Elemental Energy for him. The Wolf Within will fight alongside Razor for the skill's duration.

characters.name: Sucrose
characters.title: Knights of Favonius Alchemist
characters.description: An alchemist specializing in bio-alchemy, she also serves as an assistant for Albedo, the head alchemist of the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Wind Spirit Creation
talents.description: Performs up to 4 attacks using Wind Spirits, dealing Anemo DMG. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina and deals AoE Anemo DMG after a short casting time.

talents.name: Astable Anemohypostasis Creation - 6308
talents.description: Creates a small Wind Spirit that pulls opponents and objects towards its location, launches opponents within its AoE, and deals Anemo DMG.

talents.name: Forbidden Creation - Isomer 75 / Type II
talents.description: Sucrose hurls an unstable concoction that creates a Large Wind Spirit. While it persists, the Large Wind Spirit will continuously pull in surrounding opponents and objects, launch nearby opponents, and deal Anemo DMG.

characters.name: Xingqiu
characters.title: Guhua Guru of Feiyun Fame
characters.description: He is the second son of the Guild Manager of the Feiyun Commerce Guild, an influential group in Liyue, and is also a self-proclaimed practitioner of the Guhua Clan's arts.

talents.name: Guhua Style
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. Consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Guhua Sword: Fatai Rainscreen
talents.description: Xingqiu performs twin strikes with his sword, dealing Hydro DMG. At the same time, this ability creates the maximum number of Rain Swords, which will orbit your active character.

talents.name: Guhua Sword: Raincutter
talents.description: Initiate Rainbow Bladework and fight using an illusory sword rain, while creating the maximum number of Rain Swords. Your active character's Normal Attacks will trigger consecutive sword rain attacks, dealing Hydro DMG. Rain Swords will remain at the maximum number throughout the ability's duration.

characters.name: Diona
characters.title: Popular bartender of the Cat's Tail
characters.description: Despite being a bartender at the Cat's Tail, she loathes alcohol and will stop at nothing to ruin Mondstadt's wine industry — a feat easier said than done when her patrons absolutely love her drinks. She is the daughter of Draff, a hunter in Springvale.

talents.name: Kätzlein Style
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive shots with a bow. Performs a more precise Aimed Shot with increased DMG. While aiming, biting frost will accumulate on the arrowhead. A fully charged frost arrow will deal Cryo DMG.

talents.name: Icy Paws
talents.description: Fires an Icy Paw that deals Cryo DMG to opponents and forms a shield on hit. The shield's DMG Absorption scales based on Diona's Max HP, and its duration scales off the number of Icy Paws that hit their target.

talents.name: Signature Mix
talents.description: Tosses out a special cold brew that deals AoE Cryo DMG and creates a Drunken Mist in an AoE. Deals continuous Cryo DMG to opponents within the AoE. Continuously regenerates the HP of characters within the AoE.

characters.name: Tartaglia
characters.title: The Eleventh of the Eleven Fatui Harbingers
characters.description: Always energetic and full of life, Amber's the best - albeit only - Outrider of the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Cutting Torrent
talents.description: Performs up to 6 consecutive shots with a bow. Performs a more precise Aimed Shot with increased DMG. While aiming, the power of Hydro will accumulate on the arrowhead. An arrow fully charged with the torrent will deal Hydro DMG and apply the Riptide status.

talents.name: Foul Legacy: Raging Tide
talents.description: Unleashes a set of weaponry made of pure water, dealing Hydro DMG to surrounding opponents and entering Melee Stance. Hitting an opponent affected by Riptide with a melee attack unleashes a Riptide Slash that deals AoE Hydro DMG.

talents.name: Havoc: Obliteration
talents.description: Performs different attacks based on what stance Tartaglia is in when casting. In ranged stance, swiftly fires a Hydro-imbued magic arrow, applying the Riptide status. In melee stance, performs a slash with a large AoE that triggers Riptide Blast. Riptide blast triggers a Hydro Explosion that deals AoE Hydro DMG.

characters.name: Xinyan
characters.title: Liyue's Sole Rock 'n' Roll Musician
characters.description: Rock 'n' roll is a relatively unpopular style of music in Liyue, having recently been brought over from Fontaine. Xinyan, however, loves the sound — and she's slowly but surely amassing a fanbase of her own as she performs throughout Liyue Harbor.

talents.name: Dance on Fire
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes. Drains Stamina over time to perform continuous spinning attacks against all nearby opponents. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Sweeping Fervor
talents.description: Xinyan brandishes her instrument, dealing Pyro DMG on nearby opponents, forming a shield made out of her audience's passion. The shield's DMG Absorption scales based on Xinyan's DEF and on the number of opponents hit.

talents.name: Riff Revolution
talents.description: Strumming rapidly, Xinyan launches nearby opponents and deals Physical DMG to them, hyping up the crowd. The sheer intensity of the atmosphere will cause explosions that deal Pyro DMG to nearby opponents.

characters.name: Zhongli
characters.title: Geo Archon | Wangsheng Funeral Parlor Consultant
characters.description: A consultant of the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor, he is later revealed to be the current vessel of the Geo Archon, Morax, who has decided to experience the world from the perspective of a mortal.

talents.name: Rain of Stone
talents.description: Performs up to 6 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, causing stone spears to fall along his path.

talents.name: Dominus Lapidus
talents.description: Commands the power of earth to create a Stone Stele. When created, deals AoE Geo DMG. Additionally, it will intermittently resonate with other nearby Geo constructs, dealing Geo DMG to surrounding opponents. When charged, creates a shield of jade. The shield's DMG Absorption scales based on Zhongli's Max HP.

talents.name: Planet Befall
talents.description: Brings a falling meteor down to earth, dealing massive Geo DMG to opponents caught in its AoE and applying the Petrification status to them. Opponents affected by the Petrification status cannot move.

characters.name: Albedo
characters.title: Chief Alchemist of the Knights of Favonius
characters.description: A synthetic human made by the alchemist Rhinedottir, the mysterious Albedo is the Chief Alchemist and Captain of the Investigation Team of the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Favonius Bladework: Weiss
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Abiogenesis: Solar Isotoma
talents.description: When opponents within the Solar Isotoma field take DMG, the Solar Isotoma will generate Transient Blossoms that deal geo DMG scaling off Albedo's DEF. At the locus of the Solar Isotoma, a crystallized platform, formed from geo power, lifts the character up to a certain height.

talents.name: Rite of Progeniture: Tectonic Tide
talents.description: Under Albedo's command, Geo crystals surge and burst forth, dealing AoE Geo DMG in front of him. If a Solar Isotoma created by Albedo himself is on the field, 7 Fatal Blossoms will be generated in the Solar Isotoma field, bursting violently into bloom and dealing AoE Geo DMG.

characters.name: Ganyu
characters.title: Secretary of the Yuehai Pavilion
characters.description: She is a half-qilin Adeptus under contract with the Geo Archon Morax and serves as the general secretary of the Liyue Qixing.

talents.name: Liutian Archery
talents.description: Performs up to 6 consecutive shots with a bow. When charged, performs a more precise Aimed Shot with increased DMG. While aiming, an icy aura will accumulate on the arrowhead before the arrow is fired. Has different effects based on how long the energy has been charged.

talents.name: Trail of the Qilin
talents.description: Leaving a single Ice Lotus behind, Ganyu dashes backward, shunning all impurity and dealing AoE Cryo DMG and continuously taunting surrounding opponents. Blooms profusely when destroyed or once its duration ends, dealing AoE Cryo DMG.

talents.name: Celestial Shower
talents.description: Coalesces atmospheric frost and snow to summon a Sacred Cryo Pearl that exorcises evil. During its ability duration, the Sacred Cryo Pearl will continuously rain down shards of ice, striking opponents within an AoE and dealing Cryo DMG.

characters.name: Xiao
characters.title: Vigilant Yaksha, Bane of All Evil
characters.description: He is an adeptus, under the name Alatus, and the sole surviving member of the five foremost Yakshas dispatched by Morax to subdue the demonic spirits that plagued Liyue.

talents.name: Whirlwind Thrust
talents.description: Performs up to 6 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to perform an upward thrust.

talents.name: Lemniscatic Wind Cycling
talents.description: Xiao lunges forward, dealing Anemo DMG to opponents in his path. Can be used in mid-air.

talents.name: Bane of All Evil
talents.description: Xiao dons the Yaksha Mask that set gods and demons trembling millennia ago. Yaksha's Mask greatly increases Xiao's jumping ability and increases his attack AoE and attack DMG. In this state, Xiao will continuously lose HP.

characters.name: Hu Tao
characters.title: Director of the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor
characters.description: Hu Tao's antics and eccentricity belies her role as the 77th Director of the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor and her talent as a poet. She treats the parlor's operations with utmost importance, and holds funeral ceremonies with the highest dignity and solemnity.

talents.name: Secret Spear of Wangsheng
talents.description: Performs up to 6 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Guide to Afterlife
talents.description: Hu Tao consumes a set portion of her HP to knock the surrounding enemies back and enter the Paramita Papilio state. Increases Hu Tao's ATK based on her Max HP at the time of entering this state. Charged Attacks apply the Blood Blossom effect, causing them to take Pyro DMG every 4s.

talents.name: Spirit Soother
talents.description: Commands a blazing spirit to attack, dealing Pyro DMG in a large AoE. Regenerates a percentage of Hu Tao's Max HP on hit. If Hu Tao's HP is below or equal to 50% when the enemy is hit, both the DMG and HP Regeneration are increased.

characters.name: Rosaria
characters.title: Thorny Benevolence, A Nonconforming Sister
characters.description: The least devout among the nuns of the Church of Favonius, Rosaria prefers acting in the shadows rather than participating in the activities of the Church.

talents.name: Spear of the Church
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive spear strikes. When charged consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Ravaging Confession
talents.description: Rosaria swiftly shifts her position to appear behind her opponent, then stabs and slashes them with her polearm, dealing Cryo DMG.

talents.name: Rites of Termination
talents.description: Rosaria's unique take on this prayer ritual: First, she swings her weapon to slash surrounding opponents; then, she summons a frigid Ice Lance that strikes the ground. Both actions deal Cryo DMG. While active, the Ice Lance periodically releases a blast of cold air, dealing Cryo DMG to surrounding opponents.

characters.name: Yanfei
characters.title: Liyue Harbor's Famed Legal Adviser

weapon.signature: Lost Prayer to the Sacred Winds

characters.description: One of the few half-illuminated-beasts who have not signed a contract with Rex Lapis, Yanfei nevertheless works for the betterment of Liyue as a premier legal adviser who values fairness..

talents.name: Seal of Approval
talents.description: Shoots fireballs that deal up to three counts of Pyro DMG. When Yanfei's Normal Attacks hit enemies, they will grant her a single Scarlet Seal. Each Scarlet Seal will decrease Yanfei's Stamina consumption and will disappear when she leaves the field.

talents.name: Signed Edict
talents.description: Summons blistering flames that deal AoE Pyro DMG. Opponents hit by the flames will grant Yanfei the maximum number of Scarlet Seals.

talents.name: Done Deal
talents.description: Triggers a spray of intense flames that rush at nearby opponents, dealing AoE Pyro DMG, granting Yanfei the maximum number of Scarlet Seals, and applying Brilliance to her. Brilliance grants Yanfei a Scarlet Seal at fixed intervals and increases the DMG dealt by her Charged Attacks.

characters.name: Eula
characters.title: Dance of the Shimmering Wave, Spindrift Knight
characters.description: Although a descendant of the infamous and tyrannical Lawrence Clan, Eula severed her ties with the clan and became the captain of the Reconnaissance Company with the Knights of Favonius.

talents.name: Favonius Bladework: Edel
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive strikes. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous slashes. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Icetide Vortex
talents.description: Sharp frost, swift blade. Slashes swiftly, dealing Cryo DMG. When it hits an opponent, Eula gains a stack of Grimheart that stacks up to 2 times. These stacks can only be gained once every 0.3s. Grimheart increases Eula's resistance to interruption and DEF.

talents.name: Glacial Illumination
talents.description: Brandishes her greatsword, dealing Cryo DMG to nearby opponents and creating a Lightfall Sword that follows her around. While present, the Lightfall Sword increases Eula's resistance to interruption. When Eula's attacks deal DMG to opponents, they will charge the Lightfall Sword. Once its duration ends, the Lightfall Sword will descend and explode violently.

characters.name: Kaedehara Kazuha
characters.title: A Wandering Samurai Who Left His Homeland
characters.description: A wandering samurai of the once-famed Kaedehara Clan with an ability to read the sounds of nature, Kazuha is a temporary crewmember of The Crux. Despite being burdened by the many happenings of his past, Kazuha still maintains an easygoing disposition.

talents.name: Garyuu Bladework
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When a Plunging Attack is performed using the effects of the Elemental Skill Chihayaburu, Plunging Attack DMG is converted to Anemo DMG and will create a small wind tunnel via a secret blade technique that pulls in nearby objects and opponents.

talents.name: Chihayaburu
talents.description: Unleashes a secret technique as fierce as the rushing wind that pulls objects and opponents towards Kazuha's current position before launching opponents within the AoE, dealing Anemo DMG and lifting Kazuha into the air on a rushing gust of wind.

talents.name: Kazuha Slash
talents.description: The signature technique of Kazuha's self-styled bladework — a single slash that strikes with the force of the first winds of autumn, dealing AoE Anemo DMG. The blade's passage will leave behind a field named "Autumn Whirlwind" that periodically deals AoE Anemo DMG to opponents within its range.

characters.name: Kamisato Ayaka
characters.title: Daughter of the Kamisato Clan
characters.description: She is in charge of the internal and external affairs of the Kamisato Clan and is the younger sister of Kamisato Ayato. Beautiful, dignified, and noble, Ayaka has earned the title Shirasagi Himegimi and is considered a model of perfection in Inazuma.

talents.name: Kamisato Art: Kabuki
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash a flurry of sword ki.

talents.name: Kamisato Art: Hyouka
talents.description: Summons blooming ice to launch nearby opponents, dealing AoE Cryo DMG.

talents.name: Kamisato Art: Soumetsu
talents.description: Summons forth a snowstorm with flawless poise, unleashing a Frostflake Seki no To that moves forward continuously. This storm of whirling icy winds slashes repeatedly at every enemy it touches, dealing Cryo DMG. The snowstorm explodes after its duration ends, dealing AoE Cryo DMG.

characters.name: Sayu
characters.title: Shuumatsuban's Resident Ninja
characters.description: A ninja from the Shuumatsuban that is struggling with growing tall. Sayu believes that sleeping can help her growth, which is why she prefers to use her ninja techniques to hide and "laze around."

talents.name: Shuumatsuban Ninja Blade
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous spinning attacks against all nearby opponents. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Yoohoo Art: Fuuin Dash
talents.description: The special technique of the Yoohoo Ninja Arts! Sayu curls up into a rolling Fuufuu Windwheel and smashes into opponents at high speed, dealing Anemo DMG. When the duration ends, she unleashes a Fuufuu Whirlwind Kick, dealing AoE Anemo DMG.

talents.name: Yoohoo Art: Mujina Flurry
talents.description: The other super special technique of the Yoohoo Ninja Arts! It summons a pair of helping hands for Sayu. Deals Anemo DMG to nearby opponents and heals all nearby party members. The amount of HP restored is based on Sayu's ATK. This skill then summons a Muji-Muji Daruma.

characters.name: Yoimiya
characters.title: Owner of Naganohara Fireworks
characters.description: Yoimiya is the current owner of Naganohara Fireworks; with her colorful fireworks and outgoing personality, Yoimiya is loved by everyone on Narukami Island. She was coined as the "Queen of the Summer Festival," as they believe summer is not the same without her.

talents.name: Firework Flare-Up
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive shots with a bow. When charged, perform a more precise Aimed Shot with increased DMG. While aiming, flames will accumulate on the arrowhead before being fired off as an attack.

talents.name: Niwabi Fire-Dance
talents.description: Yoimiya waves a sparkler and causes a ring of saltpeter to surround her. During this time, arrows fired by Yoimiya's Normal Attack will be Blazing Arrows, and their DMG will be increased and converted to Pyro DMG.

talents.name: Ryuukin Saxifrage
talents.description: Yoimiya leaps into the air along with her original creation, the "Ryuukin Saxifrage," and fires forth blazing rockets bursting with surprises that deal AoE Pyro DMG and mark one of the hit opponents with Aurous Blaze.

characters.name: Kujou Sara
characters.title: General of the Tenryou Commission
characters.description: A tengu, Sara is the adopted daughter of the Kujou Clan of the Tenryou Commission. Loyal to both her clan and the Shogun, Sara carries out her orders by the Shogun's will.

talents.name: Tengu Bowmanship
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive shots with a bow.While aiming, crackling lightning will accumulate on the arrowhead. An arrow fully charged with the storm's might will deal Electro DMG. When in the Crowfeather Cover state, a fully-charged arrow will leave a Crowfeather behind after it hits.

talents.name: Tengu Stormcall
talents.description: Retreats rapidly with the speed of a tengu, summoning the protection of the Crowfeather. Gains Crowfeather Cover. Crowfeathers will trigger Tengu Juurai: Ambush after a short time, dealing Electro DMG and granting the active character within its AoE an ATK Bonus based on Kujou Sara's Base ATK.

talents.name: Subjugation: Koukou Sendou
talents.description: Casts down Tengu Juurai: Titanbreaker, dealing AoE Electro DMG. Afterwards, Tengu Juurai: Titanbreaker spreads out into 4 consecutive bouts of Tengu Juurai: Stormcluster, dealing AoE Electro DMG.

characters.name: Raiden Shogun
characters.title: The Electro Archon | Her Eternal Excellency
characters.description: The Raiden Shogun is unique as she is comprised of two beings in one body: Ei, the current Electro Archon of Inazuma; and the Shogun, the puppet created by Ei to act as the ruler of Inazuma in her stead, which also serves as her vessel.

talents.name: Origin
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive spear strikes. When charged consumes a certain amount of Stamina to perform an upward slash.

talents.name: Transcendence:,Baleful Omen
talents.description: The Raiden Shogun unveils a shard of her Euthymia, dealing Electro DMG to nearby opponents, and granting nearby party members the Eye of Stormy Judgment. When characters with this buff attack, the Eye will unleash a coordinated attack, dealing AoE Electro DMG at the opponent's position.

talents.name: Secret Art: Musou Shinsetsu
talents.description: Gathering truths unnumbered and wishes uncounted, the Raiden Shogun unleashes the Musou no Hitotachi and deals AoE Electro DMG, using Musou Isshin in combat for a certain duration afterward. The DMG dealt by Musou no Hitotachi and Musou Isshin's attacks will be increased based on the number of Chakra Desiderata's Resolve stacks consumed when this skill is used.

characters.name: Sangonomiya Kokomi
characters.title: Divine Priestess of Watatsumi Island
characters.description: The young Divine Priestess of Watatsumi Island and a descendant of the Sangonomiya Clan, Kokomi is in charge of most of Watatsumi's affairs. She works to give Watatsumi Island's people the hopes and happiness that they desire.

talents.name: The Shape of Water
talents.description: Performs up to 3 consecutive attacks that take the form of swimming fish, dealing Hydro DMG. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal AoE Hydro DMG after a short casting time.

talents.name: Kurage's Oath
talents.description: Summons a "Bake-Kurage" created from water that can heal her allies. Using this skill will apply the Wet status to Sangonomiya Kokomi. Bake-Kurage deals Hydro DMG to surrounding opponents and heal nearby active characters at fixed intervals. This healing is based on Kokomi's Max HP.

talents.name: Nereid's Ascension
talents.description: Summons the might of Watatsumi, dealing Hydro DMG to surrounding opponents, before robing Kokomi in a Ceremonial Garment made from the flowing waters of Sangonomiya. Sangonomiya Kokomi's Normal Attack, Charged Attack and Bake-Kurage DMG are increased based on her Max HP Sangonomiya Kokomi's Normal Attack, Charged Attack and Bake-Kurage DMG are increased and heal nearby allies based on her Max HP.

characters.name: Thoma
characters.title: The Kamisato Clan's Housekeeper
characters.description: Thoma is the sociable and responsible housekeeper for the Kamisato Clan and a well-known "fixer" in Inazuma. Having amassed a powerful network of people, Thoma defends the rights and interests of the Yashiro Commission with utmost seriousness.

talents.name: Swiftshatter Spear
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Blazing Blessing
talents.description: Thoma vaults forward with his polearm and delivers a flame-filled flying kick that deals AoE Pyro DMG, while also summoning a defensive Blazing Barrier. At the moment of casting, Thoma's Elemental Skill applies Pyro to himself.

talents.name: Crimson Ooyoroi
talents.description: Thoma spins his polearm, slicing at his foes with roaring flames that deal AoE Pyro DMG and weave themselves into a Scorching Ooyoroi. While Scorching Ooyoroi is in effect, the active character's Normal Attacks will trigger Fiery Collapse, dealing AoE Pyro DMG and summoning a Blazing Barrier.

characters.name: Gorou
characters.title: General of the Watatsumi Army
characters.description: He is a general of the Watatsumi Army. Courageous and reliable, his men know they can place their trust in him both on and off of the battlefield.

talents.name: Ripping Fang Fletching
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, stone crystals will accumulate on the arrowhead. A fully charged crystalline arrow will deal Geo DMG.

talents.name: Inuzaka All-Round Defense
talents.description: Deals AoE Geo DMG and sets up a General's War Banner. Provides up to 3 buffs to active characters within the skill's AoE based on the number of Geo characters in the party at the time of casting.

talents.name: Juuga: Forward Unto Victory
talents.description: Displaying his valor as a general, Gorou deals Aoe Geo DMG and creates a field known as General's Glory to embolden his comrades.

characters.name: Arataki Itto
characters.title: The First and Greatest Head of the Arataki Gang
characters.description: A loud and proud descendant of the crimson oni, Itto is also the leader and founder of the Arataki Gang. While not a villain, his reputation as a delinquent in Inazuma City leaves something to be desired.

talents.name: Fight Club Legend
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes. When the 2nd and 4th strikes hit opponents, Itto will gain 1 and 2 stacks of Superlative Superstrength, respectively.

talents.name: Masatsu Zetsugi: Akaushi Burst!
talents.description: Hurls Ushi, the young akaushi bull and auxiliary member of the Arataki Gang, dealing Geo DMG to opponents on hit. When Ushi hits opponents, Arataki Itto gains 1 stack of Superlative Superstrength.

talents.name: Royal Descent: Behold, Itto the Evil!
talents.description: Time to show 'em the might of the Arataki Gang! For a time, Itto lets out his inner Raging Oni King, wielding his Oni King's Kanabou in battle. This state converts Itto's Normal, Charged, and Plunging Attacks to Geo DMG.

characters.name: Shenhe
characters.title: Ethereal Soul Amidst the Mortal Realm
characters.description: The daughter of an unnamed exorcist couple, Shenhe was taken in and raised by Cloud Retainer as a disciple following a traumatic incident instigated by Shenhe's father during her childhood.

talents.name: Dawnstar Piercer
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Spring Spirit Summoning
talents.description: Grants all nearby party members the Icy Quill effect and deals Cryo DMG in different ways based on whether it is pressed or held. When pressed, rushes forward together with a Talisman Spirit, dealing Cryo DMG to opponents along the path. When held, commands the Talisman Spirit to deal AoE Cryo DMG.

talents.name: Divine Maiden's Deliverance
talents.description: Unleashes the power of the Talisman Spirit, allowing it to roam free in this plane, dealing AoE Cryo DMG. The Talisman Spirit then creates a field that decreases the Cryo RES and Physical RES of opponents within it. It also deals periodic Cryo DMG to opponents within the field.

characters.name: Yun Jin
characters.title: Director of Yun-Han Opera Troupe
characters.description: A famous figure in Liyue Harbor's opera scene, Yun Jin is the director of the Yun-Han Opera Troupe, and performs at Heyu Tea House from time to time. She is also a playwright, having written all the plays the Yun-Han Opera Troupe has performed in recent years.

talents.name: Cloud-Grazing Strike
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Opening Flourish
talents.description: Ms. Yun may just be acting out fights on stage, but her skills with the spear are real enough to defend against her foes. When pressed, flourishes her polearm in a cloud-grasping stance, dealing Geo DMG. When held, takes up the Opening Flourish stance and charges up, forming a shield.

talents.name: Cliffbreaker's Banner
talents.description: Deals AoE Geo DMG and grants all nearby party members a Flying Cloud Flag Formation. When Normal Attack DMG is dealt to opponents, Bonus DMG will be dealt based on Yun Jin's current DEF.

characters.name: Yae Miko
characters.title: Guuji of the Grand Narukami Shrine
characters.description: A kitsune of many facets, Yae Miko oversees the Grand Narukami Shrine, owns the Yae Publishing House, and is Eternity's servant and friend.

talents.name: Spiritfox Sin-Eater
talents.description: Summons forth kitsune spirits, initiating a maximum of 3 attacks that deal Electro DMG. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal Electro DMG after a short casting time.

talents.name: Yakan Evocation: Sesshou Sakura
talents.description: To Yae, such dull tasks as can be accomplished by driving spirits out need not be done personally. Moves swiftly, leaving a Sesshou Sakura behind. Sesshou Sakura periodically strikes one nearby opponent with lightning. When there are other Sesshou Sakura nearby, their level will increase, boosting their DMG dealt.

talents.name: Great Secret Art: Tenko Kenshin
talents.description: Legends of "kitsunetsuki," or the manifestations of a kitsune's might, are common in Inazuma's folktales. One that particularly captures the imagination is that of the Sky Kitsune, said to cause lightning to fall down upon the foes of the Grand Narukami Shrine. Summons a lightning strike, dealing AoE Electro DMG and unsealing nearby Sesshou Sakura, destroying their outer forms and transforming them into Tenko Thunderbolts that descend from the skies.

characters.name: Kamisato Ayato
characters.title: Head of the Kamisato Clan
characters.description: He is the current head of the Kamisato Clan, the older brother of Kamisato Ayaka, and the Yashiro Commissioner. Resourceful and cunning, Ayato keeps a lower profile than his sister and focuses on government affairs in the Commission.

talents.name: Kamisato Art: Marobashi
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to dash forward and perform an iai.

talents.name: Kamisato Art: Kyouka
talents.description: Kamisato Ayato shifts positions and enters the Takimeguri Kanka state. In this state, Kamisato Ayato uses his Shunsuiken to engage in blindingly fast attacks, causing DMG from his Normal Attacks to be converted into AoE Hydro DMG. After this shift, he will leave a watery illusion at his original location. After it is formed, the watery illusion will explode if opponents are nearby

talents.name: Kamisato Art: Suiyuu
talents.description: Unveils a garden of purity that silences the cacophony within. While this space exists, Bloomwater Blades will constantly rain down and attack opponents within its AoE, dealing Hydro DMG and increasing the Normal Attack DMG of characters within.

characters.name: Yelan
characters.title: Mysterious Member of the Ministry of Civil Affairs
characters.description: She is a mysterious person who claims to work for the Ministry of Civil Affairs, but comes out as a non-entity on their list. She also claims to work for the Yanshang Teahouse, but only uses it for her true job, an intelligence agent collaborating with Ningguang.

talents.name: Stealthy Bowshot
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, flowing water will accumulate on the arrowhead. A fully charged torrential arrow will deal Hydro DMG.

talents.name: Lingering Lifeline
talents.description: Fires off a Lifeline that allows her to move rapidly, entangling and marking opponents along its path. When this rapid movement ends, the Lifeline will explode, dealing Hydro DMG to the marked opponents based on Yelan's Max HP.

talents.name: Depth-Clarion Dice
talents.description: Deals AoE Hydro DMG and creates an "Exquisite Throw," which aids her in battle. The Exquisite Throw follows the character around and will initiate a coordinated attack that deals Hydro DMG based on Yelan's Max HP.

characters.name: Kuki Shinobu
characters.title: Deputy Leader of the Arataki Gang
characters.description: Kuki Shinobu is the sidekick of Arataki Itto and Deputy Leader of the Arataki Gang. Due to her professionalism and certifications, she has helped the Arataki Gang out of many problems, expanding the gang's business scope outside of the regular mischief and delinquency.

talents.name: Shinobu's Shadowsword
talents.description: Performs up to 4 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Sanctifying Ring
talents.description: Creates a Grass Ring of Sanctification at the cost of part of her HP that follows your current active character around. Deals Electro DMG to nearby opponents every 1.5s and restores HP for the active character(s) within the ring's AoE based on Kuki Shinobu's Max HP.

talents.name: Gyoei Narukami Kariyama Rite
talents.description: Stabs an evil-excoriating blade into the ground, creating a field that cleanses the area of all that is foul, dealing continuous Electro DMG to opponents within its AoE based on Shinobu's Max HP. If Shinobu's HP is less than or equal to 50% when this skill is used, the field will last longer.

characters.name: Shikanoin Heizou
characters.title: Detective of the Tenryou Commission
characters.description: He is the number one Tenryou Commission detective, harboring a rivalry with the Bantan Sango Detective Agency's Sango.

talents.name: Fudou Style Martial Arts
talents.description: Performs up to 5 fisticuffs empowered by a mighty wind, dealing Anemo DMG. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina and performs a sweeping kick that deals Anemo DMG.

talents.name: Heartstopper Strike
talents.description: Charges energy to unleash an even stronger blow. He will obtain the Declension effect while charging, which will increase the power of the Heartstopper Strike. Declension increases the power of the next Heartstopper Strike. When you possess 4 Declension stacks, the Conviction effect will be produced, which will cause the next Heartstopper Strike to be even stronger and have a larger AoE.

talents.name: Windmuster Kick
talents.description: Leaps into the air and uses the Fudou Style Vacuum Slugger and kicks his opponent. The Vacuum Slugger will explode upon hit and create an Arresting Windtunnel that pulls in nearby objects and opponents, dealing AoE Anemo DMG.

characters.name: Collei
characters.title: Avidya Forest Ranger Trainee
characters.description: Originally a victim of Fatui human experimentation, Collei wandered the world as a vagrant until she met Amber in Mondstadt. Since then, Collei has turned her life around, and currently serves as a trainee Forest Ranger in the Avidya Forest.

talents.name: Supplicant's Bowmanship
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, Dendro energy will accumulate on the arrowhead. A fully charged arrow will deal Dendro DMG.

talents.name: Floral Brush
talents.description: Throws out a Floral Ring that deals 1 instance of Dendro DMG to targets it comes into contact with. The Floral Ring will return after a set time, dealing Dendro DMG once again.

talents.name: Trump-Card Kitty
talents.description: Trusty Cuilein-Anbar comes to save the day! Throws the doll named Cuilein-Anbar, causing an explosion that deals AoE Dendro DMG, creating a Cuilein-Anbar Zone. Cuilein-Anbar will bounce around within this zone, dealing AoE Dendro DMG.

characters.name: Tighnari
characters.title: Avidya Forest Watcher
characters.description: Tighnari is the stern Chief Officer of the Forest Rangers and Collei's mentor. Despite his intelligence, he prefers to live a solitary life in the depths of Avidya Forest rather than in the ivory tower of Sumeru Akademiya.

talents.name: Khanda Barrier-Buster
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, the power of Dendro will accumulate on the arrowhead before the arrow is fired. At full charge, fires off a Wreath Arrow that deals Dendro DMG. Upon hit, the Wreath Arrow will create 4 Clusterbloom Arrows that will track nearby opponents automatically and deal Dendro DMG.

talents.name: Vijnana-Phala Mine
talents.description: Tighnari throws a Vijnana Stormheart ahead that deals AoE Dendro DMG, creating a Vijnana-Khanda Field that creates mysterious illusions that taunt opponents and draw their fire. Additionally, Tighnari gains the Vijnana Suffusion effect, which will decrease the Wreath Arrow's charging time by 2.4s.

talents.name: Fashioner's Tanglevine Shaft
talents.description: Combines the power of all seeds to fire 6 Tanglevine Shafts that can track opponents and deal Dendro DMG. After they hit, the Tanglevine Shafts will create a secondary wave of Tanglevine Shafts that can also track nearby opponents and deal Dendro DMG on hit.

characters.name: Dori
characters.title: Black Market Sumeru Merchant
characters.description: The owner of The Palace of Alcazarzaray and a merchant of high regard, "Lord Sangemah Bay" is well-known for her ability to obtain anything a person needs, as long as they have enough Mora to afford her jaw-dropping prices.

talents.name: Marvelous Sword-Dance
talents.description: Performs up to 3 consecutive strikes. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous spinning attacks against all nearby opponents. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Spirit-Warding Lamp: Troubleshooter Cannon
talents.description: Directs a Spirit-Warding Lamp to fire off a Troubleshooter Shot at opponents, dealing Electro DMG. After the Troubleshooter Shot hits, it will create 2 After-Sales Service Rounds that will automatically track nearby opponents and deal Electro DMG.

talents.name: Alcazarzaray's Exactitude
talents.description: Summons forth the Jinni within the lamp to give the client various kinds of aid. When the jinni connects to a nearby character, it continuously restores HP based on Dori's Max HP and continuously regenerates Energy. When the connector between the Jinni and the character touches opponents, it will deal one instance of Electro DMG to them every 0.4s.

characters.name: Candace
characters.title: Guardian of Aaru Village
characters.description: The scion of Al-Ahmar and the Guardian of Aaru Village, Candace is kind to travelers who visit, but is unforgiving to those who violate the village's rules.

talents.name: Gleaming Spear: Guardian Stance
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Sacred Rite: Heron's Sanctum
talents.description: Candace's fighting style is capable of warding off an entire tide of foes. Candace rushes forward with her shield, dealing Hydro DMG to opponents in front of her. When charged, she raises her shield to block incoming attacks from nearby opponents, forming a barrier that absorbs DMG based on her Max HP. When finished charging, candace performs a leaping strike that deals Hydro DMG

talents.name: Sacred Rite: Wagtail's Tide
talents.description: Raising her weapon on high, Candace calls upon a divine blessing that deals AoE Hydro DMG based on her Max HP and continuously confers the Prayer of the Crimson Crown on your active character.

characters.name: Cyno
characters.title: General Mahamatra of the Akademiya
characters.description: As the General Mahamatra, Cyno leads the Matra and strikes fear into the hearts of researchers of the Sumeru Akademiya. In spite of this, Cyno has a fun side outside of his role in the Akademiya, constantly cracking unfunny jokes.

talents.name: Invoker's Spear
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Secret Rite: Chasmic Soulfarer
talents.description: Performs a swift thrust, dealing Electro DMG to opponents along the path. When Cyno is under the Pathsworn Pathclearer state triggered by Sacred Rite: Wolf's Swiftness, he will instead unleash a Mortuary Rite that deals thunderous AoE Electro DMG and extends the duration of Pathsworn Pathclearer.

talents.name: Sacred Rite: Wolf's Swiftness
talents.description: Calls upon a divine spirit to indwell him, morphing into the Pactsworn Pathclearer. Cyno's Normal, Charged, and Plunging Attacks will be converted to Electro DMG. Cyno's Elemental Mastery and resistance to interruption will increase, and he gains immunity to Electro-Charged DMG.

characters.name: Nilou
characters.title: Star of Zubayr Theater
characters.description: A dancer under the Zubayr Theater, Nilou's dancing is but elegant and graceful — however, outside the stage's spotlight, she's just like any girl her age; warm, smiling, and friendly.

talents.name: Dance of Samser
talents.description: Performs up to 3 consecutive sword strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to perform a twirling slash.

talents.name: Dance of Haftkarsvar
talents.description: Enters the Pirouette state, dealing Hydro DMG to nearby opponents based on Nilou's Max HP. While she is in the Pirouette state, Nilou's Normal Attacks and Elemental Skill will cause her to enter the Sword Dance and Whirling Steps stances respectively.

talents.name: Dance of Abzendegi: Distant Dreams, Listening Spring
talents.description: Begins the dance of faraway dreams and springs that hear, causing a Lotus of Distant Waters to bloom, dealing AoE Hydro DMG based on Nilou's Max HP and applying the Lingering Aeon effect to all opponents hit. After an interval, opponents affected by Lingering Aeon will take Hydro DMG.

characters.name: Nahida
characters.title: Dendro Archon | Lesser Lord Kusanali
characters.description: She is the vessel of Buer, as Lesser Lord Kusanali,[5] the current Dendro Archon. Having been freed from her extensive confinement in the Sanctuary of Surasthana, she now strives to have a stronger presence in Sumeru.

talents.name: Akara
talents.description: Performs up to 4 attacks that deal Dendro DMG to opponents in front of her. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal AoE Dendro DMG to opponents in front of her.

talents.name: All Schemes to Know
talents.description: Sends forth karmic bonds of wood and tree from her side, dealing AoE Dendro DMG and marking up to 8 opponents hit with the Seed of Skandha. Opponents marked by the Seed of Skandha will be linked to one another. After you trigger Elemental Reactions on opponents or when they take DMG from Dendro Cores, Nahida will unleash Tri-Karma Purification, dealing Dendro DMG to all connected opponents.

talents.name: Illusory Heart
talents.description: Manifests the Court of Dreams and expands the Shrine of Maya. When the Shrine of Maya field is unleashed, differing effects will be separately unleashed based on the Elemental Types present within the party. If there are at least 2 party members of the same Elemental Types present when the field is deployed, the effects will be increased further.

characters.name: Layla
characters.title: Half-Awake, Half-Asleep, All Incredulous
characters.description: She is a student in the Rtawahist Darshan, specializing in Theoretical Astrology. Chronically sleep-deprived and of poor health as a result, Layla believes that "The Stars' Blessing" is the reason she wakes from sleepwalking to find her papers fully completed.

talents.name: Sword of the Radiant Path
talents.description: Performs up to 3 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: ENights of Formal Focus
talents.description: Puts forth a shield known as the Curtain of Slumber, dealing AoE Cryo DMG. The Curtain of Slumber's DMG Absorption is based on Layla's Max HP. When the shield is deployed, Layla will have Cryo applied to her briefly.

talents.name: Dream of the Star-Stream Shaker
talents.description: Unleashes a Celestial Dreamsphere that constantly fires Starlight Slugs at opponents within its AoE, dealing Cryo DMG. When a Starlight Slug hits, it will generate 1 Night Star for nearby Curtains of Slumber. Each Curtain of Slumber can gain 1 Night Star this way every 0.5s.

characters.name: Wanderer
characters.title: Tribulations Uncounted, Trials Unknowable
characters.description: The Wanderer's previous incarnation expunged his previous appellations and respective histories from Irminsul. Harboring his former self's memories after willingly regaining them, "Wanderer" is now the only title he goes by, for he has no home, kin, or destination.

talents.name: Yuuban Meigen
talents.description: Performs up to 3 attacks using wind blades, dealing Anemo DMG. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina, gathers a build up of high wind pressure, and deals AoE Anemo DMG after a short casting time.

talents.name: Hanega: Song of the Wind
talents.description: Concentrates the power of the winds to break free from the shackles of the earth, dealing AoE Anemo DMG before leaping into the air and entering the Windfavored state.

talents.name: Kyougen: Five Ceremonial Plays
talents.description: Compresses the atmosphere into a singular vacuum that grinds all troubles away, dealing multiple instances of AoE Anemo DMG. If the character is in the Windfavored state due to the skill "Hanega: Song of the Wind," Windfavored state will end after casting.

characters.name: Faruzan
characters.title: Haravatat Household Name
characters.description: She is a renowned professor of the Sumeru Akademiya and member of the Haravatat Darshan. She recently returned to the Akademiya after solving a puzzle and escaping the ruins that trapped her a century ago.

talents.name: Parthian Shotshooter
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive shots with a bow. While aiming, mighty winds will accumulate on the arrowhead. A fully charged wind arrow will deal Anemo DMG.

talents.name: Wind Realm of Nasamjnin
talents.description: Faruzan deploys a polyhedron that deals AoE Anemo DMG to nearby opponents. She will also enter the Manifest Gale state. While in the Manifest Gale state, Faruzan's next fully charged shot will consume this state and will become a Hurricane Arrow that contains high-pressure currents.

talents.name: The Wind's Secret Ways
talents.description: Faruzan deploys a Dazzling Polyhedron that unleashes a Whirlwind Pulse and deals AoE Anemo DMG. While the Dazzling Polyhedron persists, it will continuously move along a triangular path. Once it reaches each corner of that triangular path, it will unleash 1 more Whirlwind Pulse.

characters.name: Yaoyao
characters.title: Disciple of Streetward Rambler
characters.description: Hailing from a rural area not far from Qingce Village, Yaoyao grew up with nature at her side. Seeing potential in Yaoyao, Streetward Rambler took her in as her disciple, and Yaoyao left the tranquil mountains to live with her master in the bright and bustle Liyue Harbor.

talents.name: Toss 'N' Turn Spear
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive spear strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Raphanus Sky Cluster
talents.description: Calls upon "Yuegui: Throwing Mode," a special device created by a certain adeptus to help Yaoyao solve her problems. Throws out White Jade Radishes that will explode upon hitting characters or opponents, dealing Dendro DMG to opponents within a certain AoE, and healing characters within that same AoE based on Yaoyao's Max HP.

talents.name: Moonjade Descent
talents.description: At the enjoinment of a certain adeptus, Yuegui's full potential can be unleashed in an emergency, dealing Dendro DMG to nearby opponents and entering an (in some sense) unsurpassed Adeptal Legacy state.

characters.name: Alhaitham
characters.title: Sumeru Akademiya Scribe, Acting Grand Sage
characters.description: Alhaitham is a member of the Haravatat of the Sumeru Akademiya and the Akademiya's Scribe, responsible for documenting their findings and drafting ordinances. Despite his brilliance, people within the Akademiya are perplexed by Alhaitham.

talents.name: Abductive Reasoning
talents.description: Performs up to 5 rapid strikes. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 2 rapid sword strikes.

talents.name: Universality: An Elaboration on Form
talents.description: Rushes forward, dealing Dendro DMG to nearby opponents when the rush ends, causing a Chisel-Light Mirror to form. When he possesses Chisel-Light Mirrors, Alhaitham's attacks will be converted to Dendro DMG. The Chisel-Light Mirrors will unleash Projection Attacks that deal AoE Dendro DMG.

talents.name: Particular Field: Fetters of Phenomena
talents.description: Creates a Particular Binding Field and deals multiple instances of AoE Dendro DMG. If Chisel-Light Mirrors exist when this ability is unleashed, all such Mirrors will be consumed and increase the number of DMG instances dealt.

characters.name: Dehya
characters.title: Unfettered Desert Mercenary
characters.description: A fierce and strong warrior, the "Flame-Mane" Dehya is considered a legend among the Eremites for her might, passion, and conscientiousness. She aspires to deliver hope back to the sands that she considers her home.

talents.name: Sandstorm Assault
talents.description: Performs up to 4 consecutive strikes using her Claymore and her martial arts. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous slashes. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Molten Inferno
talents.description: This art of Dehya's own invention changes its method of use depending on the combat situation. Indomitable Flame deals AoE Pyro DMG, and creates a field known as Fiery Sanctum if not other sanctum is present. Ranging Flame will be unleashed should a Fiery Sanctum field already exist. Dehya will perform a leaping attack, dealing AoE Pyro DMG before recreating a Fiery Sanctum field at her new position.

talents.name: Leonine Bite
talents.description: Unleashing her burning anger and casting her inconvenient blade aside, Dehya enters the Blazing Lioness state and increases her resistance to interruption. In this state, Dehya will unleash the Flame-Mane's Fists, dealing Pyro DMG based on her ATK and Max HP. When its duration ends, she will unleash an Incineration Drive, dealing AoE Pyro DMG based on her ATK and Max HP.

characters.name: Mika
characters.title: Front-Line Land Surveyor of the Knights of Favonius
characters.description: Huffman's younger brother and the front-line surveyor of the Knights of Favonius Reconnaissance Company led by Eula, Mika diligently fulfills all his tasks efficiently and dreams of becoming an expert cartographer in the future.

talents.name: Spear of Favonius - Arrow's Passage
talents.description: Performs up to 5 consecutive strikes using his crossbow and spear. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to lunge forward, dealing damage to opponents along the way.

talents.name: Starfrost Swirl
talents.description: Mika uses his crossbow to attack, granting all nearby characters in your party Soulwind. When characters in the Soulwind state are on the field, their ATK SPD will be increased.

talents.name: Skyfeather Song
talents.description: Derives the ability to spur his teammates on from the recited prayers of the knightly order, regenerating HP for all nearby party members and granting them the Eagleplume state. In this state, Normal Attacks of active characters will regenerate HP based on Mika's Max HP.

characters.name: Kaveh
characters.title: Renowned Sumeru Architect
characters.description: The architect behind the Palace of Alcazarzaray, Kaveh was a student of the Kshahrewar Darshan of the Sumeru Akademiya and graduated with honors, earning the moniker "Light of Kshahrewar."

talents.name: Schematic Setup
talents.description: Uses Mehrak to perform up to 4 consecutive attacks. When charged, drains Stamina over time to perform continuous slashes. At the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.

talents.name: Artistic Ingenuity
talents.description: Uses Mehrak's mapping ability for offensive purposes, initiating a radial scan that deals AoE Dendro DMG. It will also scan all Dendro Cores in its AoE and cause them to immediately burst.

talents.name: Painted Dome
talents.description: Completely unleashes Mehrak's energy and creates a cubic scanned space, dealing AoE Dendro DMG to all opponents within it, causing all Dendro Cores in its AoE to immediately burst, and granting Kaveh enhanced combat abilities.

characters.name: Baizhu
characters.title: Owner of Bubu Pharmacy
characters.description: The owner of Bubu Pharmacy and Qiqi's guardian, Doctor Baizhu is a master of the medicinal arts and the latest recipient of a generational contract with a white snake named Changsheng.

talents.name: The Classics of Acupuncture
talents.description: Performs up to 4 attacks that deal Dendro DMG to opponents in front of him. When charged, consumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal AoE Dendro DMG to opponents in front of him after a short casting time.

talents.name: Universal Diagnosis
talents.description: Controls a Gossamer Sprite that cruises and attacks nearby opponents, dealing Dendro DMG. After it performs 3 attacks or if there are no opponents nearby, the Sprite will return, healing all nearby party members based on Baizhu's Max HP.

talents.name: Holistic Revivification
talents.description: Enters the Pulsing Clarity state, creating a Seamless Shield. While in this state, Baizhu will generate a new Seamless Shield every 2.5s. The Seamless Shield will heal your own active character based on Baizhu's Max HP and attack opponents by unleashing Spiritveins, dealing Dendro DMG.

characters.name: Kirara
characters.title: Gold Level Courier of the Komaniya Express
characters.description: A youkai — a nekomata, specifically — Kirara is the Gold Level Courier of the Inazuma-based Komaniya Express. Her diligence in ensuring every package would be delivered to the right place has increased her company's renown.

talents.name: Boxcutter
talents.description: Performs up to 4 rapid strikes. When charged, onsumes a certain amount of Stamina to unleash 3 rapid claw strikes.

talents.name: Meow-teor Kick
talents.description: Leaps into the air with all the agility of a cat passing through the bushes, and thwacks her foes with a flying kick that deals AoE Dendro DMG while creating a Shield of Safe Transport. This will also briefly apply Dendro to Kirara.

talents.name: Secret Art: Surprise Dispatch
talents.description: Smash opponents with a Special Delivery Package used for punishing parcel thieves, dealing AoE Dendro DMG. After the Special Delivery Package explodes, it will split up into many Cat Grass Cardamoms that will explode either upon contact with opponents or after a period of time, dealing AoE Dendro DMG.
